  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fairmont rooms</strong> have one king size bed, one queen size bed, two double beds, or two twin beds<strong><br /></strong></p>
<p><strong>Deluxe rooms</strong> (sleep 1-4) feature the same bed arrangements as Fairmont rooms with additional space and comfort</p>
<p><strong>Fairmont Mountain view</strong> and <strong>Deluxe Mountain view </strong>rooms are available at supplement and enjoy spectacular mountain views</p>
<p>All rooms are allocated with sufficient beds for the number of occupants and have bath and shower</p>
<p><strong>Fairmont Gold rooms</strong> are<span> privately located on the 4th and 5th floors of the main building.</span> They have a shower and one king size bed</p>
<p><strong>Fairmont Gold Mountain view rooms</strong> are available on request</p>
